videos.headline: Clemson's Beaux Collins makes juggling catch on sideline
videos.description: D.J. Uiagalelei rolls out to his right to fire a pass to Beaux Collins that he somehow tips and catches in a crowd of defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson's Beaux Collins makes juggling catch on sideline) 2021/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Will Shipley runs in for 12-yard Clemson TD
videos.description: Will Shipley follows his blockers and gets to the outside to score an easy 12-yard touchdown to give Clemson a 13-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Will Shipley runs in for 12-yard Clemson TD) 2021/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: This Clemson pick-six might be the wildest of 2021
videos.description: Brock Purdy has his pass deflected and then tips it himself to Mario Goodrich in a wild sequence of events that ends in an 18-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (This Clemson pick-six might be the wildest of 2021) 2021/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brock Purdy finds Charlie Kolar for an Iowa State TD
videos.description: Brock Purdy completes a pass to Charlie Kolar in the back of the end zone for an easy 6-yard Iowa State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brock Purdy finds Charlie Kolar for an Iowa State TD) 2021/12/29 ESHEET
